Module org.example.camping2
Package org.example.camping2.dto

Class Cliente

java.lang.Object
org.example.camping2.dto.Cliente
@Entity public class Cliente extends Object
Entity representing a client in the camping system. This class holds the personal information of a client such as name, surname, DNI, email, phone number, birth date, status, and comments. It also includes a set of associated reservations. The entity is mapped to the `cliente` table in the database.
Since:
31/01/2025
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Andrews Dos Ramos
